OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784207919
OL,3,CPolice warning after drone briefly
OL,4,Cshuts airport runway
OL,6,FPeople are being urged to "use your
OL,7,Fcommon sense" after a drone sighting
OL,8,Fnear Jersey Airport saw the runway
OL,9,Ftemporarily shut.
OL,11,FIt happened on Monday morning (13
OL,12,FJuly) and Ports of Jersey say
OL,13,F"operations were briefly paused while
OL,14,FStates of Jersey Police and the
OL,15,FAirport Fire Service investigated".
OL,17,FThey add that "normal operations
OL,18,Fresumed after a brief delay" and "the
OL,19,Fsafe and secure operation of the
OL,20,Fairport is always our first priority".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/3
