CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784207919
OL,3,CPolice warning after drone briefly
OL,4,Cshuts airport runway
OL,6,FIt is illegal to fly a drone within
OL,7,Ftwo nautical miles of the island's
OL,8,Fairport without permission from Jersey
OL,9,FAir Traffic Control (ATC).
OL,11,FSt Brelade Honorary Police say the
OL,12,F"penalties for endangering and
OL,13,Fdisrupting civil aviation are severe".
OL,15,FIn a social media post following the
OL,16,Fincident, they shared the Ports of
OL,17,FJersey 'Drone Code' - which lists the
OL,18,Fmeasures people must take to ensure
OL,19,Ftheir activities are safe and legal.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/3
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
