PN,35503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F355A1784207919
OL,3,CPolice warning after drone briefly
OL,4,Cshuts airport runway
OL,6,FThis includes not flying higher than
OL,7,F400 feet without permission from ATC
OL,8,Fand not operating a drone in any way
OL,9,Fthat could endanger people or property.
OL,11,FIt stresses: "Use your common sense
OL,12,Fand fly safely; You could be
OL,13,Fprosecuted if you don't."
OL,15,FMore information about the rules can
OL,16,Fbe found on the CI drone safety
OL,17,Fwebsite.
OL,19,FUK and European drone regulations do
OL,20,Fnot cover the Channel Islands, which
OL,21,Fhave their own sets of laws.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/3
